    <title>CKAN: Ticket #812: Package edit form only allows three extra fields</title>
    <link>http://localhost/ticket/812</link>
    <description>&lt;p&gt;
The package edit form is restricted to three extra fields. To enter more than three fields, one has to save the package and hit edit again (or hit preview).
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
A mechanism similar to the one for resources (where you can add lines as you go) would solve this. So, have a button that adds more extra field rows via JS.
&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
